Intro.1.Sec=THIS AGREEMENT made and entered into as of {AGT.Effective.YMD}, by and between {P1.N,E,A} ("{P1.Handle}&rdquo;), and {P2.N,E,A} ("{P2.Handle}&rdquo;).
